data.text: Trilogy Independent Percussion or TIP, is a separate organization that competes in the Percussion Independent A class of WGI and CWEA. This ensemble is made up entirely of students from Anderson School District 1. This group is the reigning CWEA Gold Medalist in the PIA class and plans on competing in WGI nationals in the 2024 season. This group is open to all students at Palmetto who play percussion or keyboard instruments.
